vCounter: Contador de columnas utilizado en el armado de la planilla
vCuponID: Numero de cupon utilizado para obtener datos de eventos locales
vDia: Dia de ejecucion del proceso
vMes: Mes de ejecucion del proceso
vFecha: Fecha de ejecucion del proceso
vRow: Numero de la fila que se esta cargando en el Excel
vSecuenciaTRN: Numero de secuencia para buscar el cupon correspondiente

SELECT
TE.CC03FecVen  AS FECHA_VENCIMIENTO,
RCL.CC01USANCC AS ANALISTA_CC,
RCL.CC01ENTCOD AS ENTIDAD_AZUL,
TE.CC08INTEVE AS DEBCRE,
RCL.CC01RCLID AS NRO_RECLAMO,
TRN.CC02SECTRA AS SECUENCIA_TRN,
TMP.G1NRORCL AS EXPTE,
RCL.CC01TRJNRO  AS NRO_TARJETA,
'NO APLICA' AS USUARIO,
TRN.CC02DESOPE AS COMERCIO,
TRN.CC02COTIZA AS COTIZACION,
EV.CC06MOEVID AS COD_MOTIVO,
TE.CC03OBSEVE AS ACCION,
RCL.CC01MARCOD AS MARCA,
ev.CC07MarCod AS EVENTO_MARCA,
EV.CC07MaEvId AS EVENTO,
TRN.CC02ImpLiq AS IMPORTE_LIQ,
trn.CC02MONORI AS MONEDA_ORIGEN,
trn.CC02ImpOri AS IMPORTE_ORI,
trn.CC02CodAut AS COD_AUTORIZACION,
trn.CC02FecPro as FECHA_PROCESO,
TRN.CC02ORITRA as ORIGEN_TRN
FROM GXPRDTA.CCT003 TE 
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT003 EV  
ON TE.CC01RCLID = EV.CC01RCLID AND TE.CC02SECTRA = EV.CC02SECTRA AND TE.CC03SECREL = EV.CC03SECEVE
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT002 TRN 
	ON EV.CC01RCLID = TRN.CC01RCLID AND EV.CC02SECTRA = TRN.CC02SECTRA
		JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT001 RCL  
		ON TRN.CC01RCLID = RCL.CC01RCLID 
			JOIN GXPRDTA.TRT050 TMP 
			ON TRN.CC01RCLID = TMP.TR50RCLID AND TRN.CC02SECTRA = TMP.TR50SECRCL
WHERE TE.CC08INTEVE IN (983, 982) AND TRN.CC02ORITRA <> 'DO' AND TE.CC03FecVen = $vFecha$ AND EV.CC03FECPRO >= '20190925' AND (RCL.CC01USANCC = 'GUZMAN' OR RCL.CC01USANCC = 'FSANABRIA' OR RCL.CC01USANCC = 'HCARDOZO')
ORDER BY RCL.CC01USANCC, RCL.CC01ENTCOD, TE.CC08INTEVE, RCL.CC01MARCOD, RCL.CC01RCLID

SELECT
	TE.CC03FecVen AS FECHA_VENCIMIENTO,
	RCL.CC01USANCC AS ANALISTA_CC,
	RCL.CC01ENTCOD AS ENTIDAD_AZUL,
	TE.CC08INTEVE AS DEBCRE,
	RCL.CC01RCLID AS NRO_RECLAMO,
	TRN.CC02SECTRA AS SECUENCIA_TRN,
	TMP.G1NRORCL AS EXPTE,
	RCL.CC01TRJNRO AS NRO_TARJETA,
	'NO APLICA' AS USUARIO,
	TRN.CC02DESOPE AS COMERCIO,
	TRN.CC02COTIZA AS COTIZACION,
	EV.CC06MOEVID AS COD_MOTIVO,
	TE.CC03OBSEVE AS ACCION,
	RCL.CC01MARCOD AS MARCA,
	ev.CC07MarCod AS EVENTO_MARCA,
	EV.CC07MaEvId AS EVENTO,
	TRN.CC02ImpLiq AS IMPORTE_LIQ,
	trn.CC02MONORI AS MONEDA_ORIGEN,
	trn.CC02ImpOri AS IMPORTE_ORI,
	trn.CC02CodAut AS COD_AUTORIZACION,
	trn.CC02FecPro AS FECHA_PROCESO,
	TRN.CC02ORITRA AS ORIGEN_TRN,
	RCL.CC01USUALT AS USUARIO_ALTA
FROM
	GXPRDTA.CCT003 TE
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT003 EV  
ON
	TE.CC01RCLID = EV.CC01RCLID
	AND TE.CC02SECTRA = EV.CC02SECTRA
	AND TE.CC03SECREL = EV.CC03SECEVE
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT002 TRN 
	ON
	EV.CC01RCLID = TRN.CC01RCLID
	AND EV.CC02SECTRA = TRN.CC02SECTRA
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT001 RCL  
		ON
	TRN.CC01RCLID = RCL.CC01RCLID
JOIN GXPRDTA.TRT050 TMP 
			ON
	TRN.CC01RCLID = TMP.TR50RCLID
	AND TRN.CC02SECTRA = TMP.TR50SECRCL
WHERE
	TE.CC08INTEVE IN (983, 982)
	AND TRN.CC02ORITRA <> 'DO'
	AND TE.CC03FecVen = $vFecha$
	AND EV.CC03FECPRO >= '20190925'
	AND NOT EXISTS (
		SELECT 1
		FROM GXPRDTA.GPT004 TARJ
		WHERE RCL.CC01TRJNRO = TARJ.GP04TRJNRO
	)
ORDER BY
	RCL.CC01USANCC,
	RCL.CC01ENTCOD,
	TE.CC08INTEVE,
	RCL.CC01MARCOD,
	RCL.CC01RCLID

SELECT
TE.CC03FECVEN AS FECHAVENCIMIENTO,
RCL.CC01USANCC AS ANALISTA_CC,
RCL.CC01ENTCOD AS ENTIDAD_AZUL,
TE.CC08INTEVE AS DEBCRE,
RCL.CC01RCLID AS NRO_RECLAMO,
TMP.G1NRORCL AS EXPTE,
TARJ.GP04TRJNRO AS NRO_TARJETA,
TRN.CC02SECTRA AS SECUENCIA,
TARJ.GP04TRJNOM AS USUARIO,
TRN.CC02DESOPE AS COMERCIO,
CLI.GE24CODPRO AS COD_PROCESADORA,
EV.CC06MOEVID AS COD_MOTIVO,
TE.CC03OBSEVE AS ACCION,
RCL.CC01MARCOD AS MARCA,
ev.CC07MarCod AS EVENTO_MARCA,
EV.CC08INTEVE AS EVENTO_INTERNO,
EV.CC03ObsEve AS OBSERVACION_EVENTO,
EV.CC07MaEvId AS EVENTO,
TRN.CC02ImpLiq AS IMPORTE_LIQ,
trn.CC02CodAut AS COD_AUTORIZACION,
TRN.CU03CupId AS CUPON_ID,
trn.CC02FecPro as FECHA_PROCESO
FROM GXPRDTA.CCT003 TE JOIN
GXPRDTA.CCT003 EV  --- JOIN EVENTO DE TE Y EVENTO QUE ORIGINA LA TE
ON TE.CC01RCLID = EV.CC01RCLID AND TE.CC02SECTRA = EV.CC02SECTRA AND TE.CC03SECREL = EV.CC03SECEVE
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT002 TRN   --- JOIN EVENTO TRANSACION
ON EV.CC01RCLID = TRN.CC01RCLID AND EV.CC02SECTRA = TRN.CC02SECTRA
JOIN GXPRDTA.CCT001 RCL  --- JOIN TRANSACION RCLAMO
ON TRN.CC01RCLID = RCL.CC01RCLID 
JOIN GXPRDTA.TRT050 TMP  --- JOIN TRANSACCION RELACION RCLAMO
ON TRN.CC01RCLID = TMP.TR50RCLID AND TRN.CC02SECTRA = TMP.TR50SECRCL -- JOIN
JOIN GXPRDTA.GPT004 TARJ  --- JOIN TRANSACCION TARJETA
ON RCL.CC01TRJNRO = TARJ.GP04TRJNRO
JOIN GXGEDTA.GET024 CLI ON TRN.CC02CliCod = CLI.GE23CLICOD AND TRN.CC02CliSuc = CLI.GE24CLISUC
WHERE TE.CC08INTEVE IN (983, 982) AND TRN.CC02ORITRA = 'DO' AND TE.CC03FecVen = $vFecha$ LIMIT 10
ORDER BY RCL.CC01USANCC, RCL.CC01ENTCOD, TE.CC08INTEVE
